---
title: Gochujang-Glazed Pork Chops with Savoury Sesame Noodle Stir-Fry
description: Tender pork chops smothered in a sweet and spicy Korean-style glaze are the perfect pairing for oodles of noodles packed with nutty and savoury flavours!
